      • LOWER_CASE_WITH_SPACES

        public static final JsonVariableNaming LOWER_CASE_WITH_SPACES
        Using this naming strategy with Gson will ensure that the field name is lower case and separated by spaces

        Here's a few examples of the form "Java Field Name" ---> "JSON Field Name":

        • someFieldName ---> some field name
        • _someFieldName ---> _some field name
        • aStringField ---> a string field
        • aURL ---> a u r l
